  "title": "DÆDΛLUS",
  "description": "The Official Modpack of the Eqqo Builds series.",
  "body": "<center>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/840b59e0dc95845c3656d367f612e995a5afb5b0.png\" width=\"400\"><br>\n  The <b>Official Modpack</b> of the <b>Eqqo Builds</b> Series\n  <br><br>•<br><br>\n  A Modpack designed for aesthetic immersion with vast landscapes and creative potential\n  <br><br><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d8f913297f94364481583dfcb4c87adbf5b03c9.png\"><br><br>\n  <font size=\"6\"><strong>Environment & Worldgen</strong></font>\n  <br><br><br>\n  <a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/wwoo\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8cfc2c87a4dda0489327bc5f71b83ec177d5ec81.png\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Overhauled Biomes</h3>\n  Expansive reworked biomes for a more <b>realistic, atmospheric</b> world\n<br><br>•<br><br>\n  <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/data-pack/jjthunder-king-of-the-hills/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7adc9538a29a08e3e72557e6b9570e5246c80f05.png\" alt=\"JJThunder's King of The Hills Datapack\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Vast Mountainous Terrain</h3>\n  World height increased to <b>1024<br>Immense mountains</b> and <b>rolling hills</b> cover the land\n  <br><br>•<br><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/block-swap\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8f44e070bb5a43e7fbeb4047f3425b0d72ed37a2_0.webp\" alt=\"Large Ore Veins\" width=\"650\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Huge Ore Veins</h3>\n  Great pockets of <b>Ore</b> await to be discovered underground\n  <br><br>•<br><br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/amplified-nether\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/78716fc777dd4597e978a010b8350f916fb7ff49_0.webp\" alt=\"Nether Generation\" width=\"650\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Amplified Nether</h3>\n  Now a vast open <b>hellscape</b> choked in a sulphurous haze<br><br>Increased world height, no nether ceiling and an adjusted dimension ratio of <b>1:1</b>, to encourage <b>overworld travel</b><br><br><br><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d8f913297f94364481583dfcb4c87adbf5b03c9.png\"><br><br>\n<font size=\"6\"><strong>Game Mechanics</strong></font>\n<br><br><br>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2d800fffc92de33b3548a1c501e00919337ee5cf.png\" alt=\"Create Mod\" width=\"650\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Freedom to Create</h3>\n  <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric\">Create</a></b> expands the possibilites with aesthetic functional and moving contraptions<br><br>\n  <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/create-steam-n-rails\">Steam 'n' Rails</a></b> expansion increases the depth of <b>Create's</b> rail network & steam system<br>\n  And <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/create-enchantment-industry-fabric\">Enchantment Industry</a></b> offers more tools and methods to handle <b>Experience & Enchantment</b><br><br>\n  <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/create_oxidized\">Create Oxidized</a></b> for <b>Oxidized Copper</b> automation<br>\n  And <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/create-structures\">Create Structures</a></b> implementing naturally generated <b>Structures</b> into the world\n<br><br>•<br><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/time-control\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/21d55829251880c61046340d4f92f04acbbda63e.png\" alt=\"Time Control\" width=\"650\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Long Days</h3>\n  Days and nights are now both <b>60 Minutes</b> long, for a <b>2 Hour</b> sun cycle<br><br>\n  Take your time\n<br><br>•<br><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/autohud\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/57816612c5e0ccb6551596d76e099c0c222bc48d.png\" alt=\"Auto HUD\" width=\"650\">\n  </a>\n  <h3>Clean Immersion</h3>\n  The <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/autohud\">Auto HUD</a></b> and <b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/dynamiccrosshair\">Dynamic Crosshair</a></b> mods hide the <b>Hotbar</b> and UI elements for full immersion<br><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/crunchy-crunchy-advancements\">Advancements</a></b> and their notifications are also hidden\n<br><br><br><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d8f913297f94364481583dfcb4c87adbf5b03c9.png\"><br><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/eqqo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d28e6727b2ff4e39b36ceb83cda5e5539c67827.png\" width=\"100\"></a><br><br>\n<strong><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/eqqo\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;P A T R E O N&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;•</strong></a><br><br><br>\n</center>\n",
